            "text": " قَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:50:10",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) فِي الْقَسَامَةِ خَمْسُونَ رَجُلًا فِي الْعَمْدِ وَ فِي الْخَطَإِ خَمْسَةٌ وَ عِشْرُونَ رَجُلًا وَ عَلَيْهِمْ أَنْ يَحْلِفُوا بِاللَّهِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Abdullah Bin Sinan who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said regarding the compurgation (sworn endorsements) being fifty men regarding the deliberate (killing), and regarding the erroneous, being twenty-five men, and upon them is that they should be swearing by Allah<sup>azwj</sup>’."
        ]
      }
    }
